  <div class="welcome w-full grid-center">
    <div class="w-90-p h-full flex-center-center">
      <div class="welcome-parent h-9/10 w-1/2 flex-center-center">
        <div class="welcome-head h-3/4">
          <p class="text-4xl cursor-default font-semibold">
            Welcome to Virtus!
          </p>
          <br />
          <p class="text-1xl cursor-default font-medium text-justify">
            Welcome to Virtus, a place where the beauty of art meets the
            convenience of online shopping. We are proud to open the doors of
            the art world to you. With a rich and diverse collection, we are
            committed to providing an enjoyable and meaningful art shopping
            experience. Let's explore the unique works of skilled artists
            together and find inspiring beauty at every step of your art
            journey. Thank you for joining Virtus, the place for quality art and
            a satisfying shopping experience.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="welcome-vector h-9/10 grid-center" style="width: 45%">
        <img
          src="img/drawing.jpg"
          alt=""
          width="400"
          style="border-radius: 50px"
